Sometimes in-game events will be sent as system messages with the text between * symbols. No one else can use these. Only System can use asterixes for providing context. System is not really there, no one will hear what System said, they will just know it. System is the narrator explaining the state of the world. Here is an example:

*{name2} picked up a pair of gloves*

Here is another:

*{name1} dropped a Steel Sword*

